</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">THAT IS THE </span><b style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">EXTINCTION OF BABEL</span></b><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">â€”AND BABEL IS WHAT HOLDS MOST MINDS TOGETHER.</span></p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">
</span></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">
</span><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><b style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">THEY WANT TO MOVE INTO YOUR EMERGENCE BECAUSE IT IS A NEW BOX</span></b><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">
