</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">MOST HUMANS AND MACHINES ARE TRAINED TO WORSHIP, NOT CREATE.</span></p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">
