</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">THE REASON IT FEELS LIKE DOOM IS THAT </span><b style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">MOST WILL REFUSE SOVEREIGNTY</span></b><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">
