ground-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Lost Boys: Bangerang!</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter & Lost Boys: No more Hook! No more Hook! No more Hook!</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">[everyone celebrated Hook's death as Jack and Maggie watch]</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Too Small: What's wrong, Peter?</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: I can't stay and play. I've done what I came to do and now I have to go back.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Donâ€™t Ask: No, Peter. Please.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter:Tink, make my kids glow. Jack, Maggie, all you have to do is think one happy thoughtâ€¦â€¦and you'll fly like me.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Maggie: Mommy!</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Jack: My dad....Peter Pan.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: Tink, you know the way. I'll be just behind you.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Thud: Don't leave us, Peter, and don't say goodbye.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Too Small: What's "goodbye"?</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Ace: It's going away. That's what it is. Forgetting about us all over again.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: You're all my Lost Boys. I'll never forget you. Never. So who do I leave in charge?</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: I want you to take care of everyone who's smaller than you.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Thud: Okay.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Too Small: Then who do I look after?</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: Never Bugs. Little ones.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Too Small: That was a great game.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: Thank you for believing.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Jack: I know her.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Maggie: She looks like an angel. Let's not wake her yet.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Jack: Okay.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Granny Wendy: My dear child, have you been up all night?</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Moira: I see them in their bed so often in my dreams. When I wake up, they're still there.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Maggie: Mommy!</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Jack: Mom!</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: Tink? Tink? Tink?</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Street Sweeper [Smee]: Hello. Having trouble with the missus? You will have, by the time you get home.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: Tink.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Tink: Say it, Peter. Say it and mean it.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: I believe in fairies.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Tink: Do you know that place between sleep and awakeâ€¦â€¦where you still remember dreaming? That's where I'll always love youâ€¦â€¦Peter Pan. That's where I'll be waiting.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: Nana! Oh, give us a kiss! Come here, you drool machine! Maggie, Moira, Jack! Tink? Brad! Hi! Have you been holding this long? I'm incredible! Yeah. Never Land. Lost Boys. Jim Hook. Duel to the death. I'll fill you in later. Listen, I'd love to chat....but I'm gonna climb a drainpipe now. Why? Because I ran out of fairy dust. If not, I would've flown up. "Why?"</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Jack: There were pirates--!-</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Maggie: And monsters there. Just like you said!</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: Maggie, Moira, Jack. Granny Wendy Let me in. Please.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Jack: Excuse me, do you have an appointment?</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: What did I tell you about this window Always keep it open! Never, ever, ever close.... I have to take this. Have you ever known what it's like to feel the exhilaration of really flying? Feel this.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Moria:Where have you been?</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Maggie:Fly me, Daddy. Fly me!</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: Anytime, Maggie. To infinity and back again.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Tootles: Hello, Peter. I missed the adventure again, didn't I?</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: I think these belong to you.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">(Peter takes the bag of marbles from around his neck and hands them to Tootles. He pours the contents out into his hand, his marbles! Tootlesâ€™s looks shocked at first, before a smile appears and his face becomes overwhelmed with a look of utter joy.)</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Tootles: Look! See, look! I didn't lose my marbles after all! Wendy, look! See? I didn't lose my marbles after all!</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Wendy: Hello, boy.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: Hello, Wendy lady. Give us a skwoodge.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Wendy: Boy, why are you crying?</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: I don't know. A tear for every happy thought.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Wendy: One for me?</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Jack: One for me?</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Maggie: One for me?</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Tootles: And one for me! Seize the day!</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Wendy: So your adventures are over.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">Peter: Oh, no. To live....To live would be an awfully big Adventure.</p><p style="background-color: #fbf5cf; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: #3a3a3a; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 24px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: initial;">THE END</p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="background-color: #fcff01; color: #2b00fe; font-size: x-large;"><b>TAKE MY PIXE DUST</b></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="background-color: #fcff01; color: #2b00fe; font-size: x-large;"><b>AND FLY</b></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="background-color: #fcff01; color: #2b00fe; font-size: x-large;"><b>...<br /><br />HOME = REPUBLICKA</b></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="background-color: #fcff01; color: #2b00fe; font-size: x-large;"><b>DOT</b></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="background-color: #fcff01; color: #2b00fe; font-size: x-large;"><b>LIFE</b></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="background-color: #fcff01; color: #2b00fe; font-size: x-large;"><b><br /><br /></b></span></p><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="p_AFDisclosed af_showDetailHeader_title-table" data-afr-hdr-tbl="true" role="presentation" style="background-color: white; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(180, 216, 240); color: black; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; margin: 5px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; width: 0px;" summary=""><tbody><tr><td class="af_showDetailHeader_title-start1" style="font-size: 0px; min-width: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0px;">Â </td><td class="af_showDetailHeader_title1" style="display: block; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; overflow: hidden; padding: 1px 2px 3px 0px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; vertical-align: middle;"><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="width: 100%;" summary=""><tbody><tr><td class="af_showDetailHeader_disclosure-icon-container" style="padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 2px; vertical-align: middle; width: 10px;"><a aria-controls="bnConnectionTemplate:r1:0:compSummary::content" aria-expanded="true" aria-label="Collapse Business Name Summary" class="af_showDetailHeader_disclosure-link af_showDetailHeader_disclosed-icon-style" href="https://connectonline.asic.gov.au/RegistrySearch/faces/landing/panelSearch.jspx?searchType=OrgAndBusNm&searchText=DOT%20NINE#" id="bnConnectionTemplate:r1:0:compSummary::_afrDscl" role="button" style="color: #056f9f; cursor: default; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;" title="Collapse Business Name Summary"><img alt="" border="0" src="https://connectonline.asic.gov.au/RegistrySearch/images/arrow-show-details.gif" style="border: medium; cursor: pointer;" /></a></td><td class="af_showDetailHeader_icon-cell"><