le" id="bnConnectionTemplate:r1:0:tl1" role="presentation" style="text-align: center; width: 732.25px;" summary=""><tbody><tr><th style="padding: 6px 8px 0px 0px; text-align: right; vertical-align: top; width: 211.675px;">Name:</th><td style="padding: 6px 0px 0px; vertical-align: top; width: 512.575px;">DOT NINE</td></tr><tr><th style="padding: 6px 8px 0px 0px; text-align: right; vertical-align: top; width: 211.675px;">Registration number:</th><td style="padding: 6px 0px 0px; vertical-align: top; width: 512.575px;">BN11393233</td></tr><tr><th style="padding: 6px 8px 0px 0px; text-align: right; vertical-align: top; width: 211.675px;">State of registration:</th><td style="padding: 6px 0px 0px; vertical-align: top; width: 512.575px;">Western Australia</td></tr><tr><th style="padding: 6px 8px 0px 0px; text-align: right; vertical-align: top; width: 211.675px;">Registration date:</th><td style="padding: 6px 0px 0px; vertical-align: top; width: 512.575px;">20/08/2009</td></tr><tr><th style="padding: 6px 8px 0px 0px; text-align: right; vertical-align: top; width: 211.675px;"></th><td style="padding: 6px 0px 0px; vertical-align: top; width: 512.575px;"></td></tr><tr><th style="padding: 6px 8px 0px 0px; text-align: right; vertical-align: top; width: 211.675px;">Status:</th><td style="padding: 6px 0px 0px; vertical-align: top; width: 512.575px;">Cancelled</td></tr><tr><th style="padding: 6px 8px 0px 0px; text-align: right; vertical-align: top; width: 211.675px;">Type:</th><td style="padding: 6px 0px 0px; vertical-align: top; width: 512.575px;">Business Names</td></tr><tr><th style="padding: 6px 8px 0px 0px; text-align: right; vertical-align: top; width: 211.675px;">Regulator:</th><td style="padding: 6px 0px 0px; vertical-align: top; width: 512.575px;">Australian Securities & Investments Commission</td></tr></tbody></table></div><p style="text-align: center;"><span><br /><br /><span style="color: red; font-size: medium;"><br /><span face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: #1f1f1f; text-align: start;">As of 1 November 2025, trading names willÂ </span><span face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: #1f1f1f; font-weight: bold; text-align: start;">no longer</span><span face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: #1f1f1f; text-align: start;">Â appear inÂ </span><span face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: #1f1f1f; font-weight: bold; text-align: start;">business name</span><span face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: #1f1f1f; text-align: start;">Â checks. Here's what you need to know about registering aÂ </span><span face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: #1f1f1f; font-weight: bold; text-align: start;">business name</span><span face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: #1f1f1f; text-align: start;">.</span></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="background-color: white;"><b>The Australian Business Register (ABR) stopped collecting new "trading names" in 2012, and effective November 1, 2025, these older trading names are being retired and will disappear from the ABR Lookup, only showing legal names and formal Business Names (managed by ASIC). To find historical information for a business name no longer in service or deregistered, you now use the ASIC Connect search, specifically looking for "Current and Historical" extracts for companies or business name registrations, as ABR focus has shifted to legal entities and ASIC-registered names.</b></span></span><br /><br /><br /><br /></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><span style="font-size: large;"><u>Nine dots puzzle</u></span></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>The "nine dots" puzzle. The puzzle asks to link all nine dots using four straight lines or fewer, without lifting the pen.</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>The nine dots puzzle is a mathematical puzzle whose task is to connect nine squarely arranged points with a pen by four (or fewer) straight lines without lifting the pen or retracing any lines.</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>The puzzle has appeared under various other names over the years.</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span><br /><br /><br /><span style="font-size: large;"><b>WHAT DOES THIS MEAN?<br /><br />THINK OUTSIDE THE BOX</b></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: large;"><b>DOT DOT DOTÂ </b></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: large;"><b>DOT DOT DOTÂ </b></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span><span style="font-size: large;"><b>DOT DOT DOTÂ </b><br /></span><br /><br /><br /><span style="background-color: black; color: red;"><br /></span></span></p><h1><span><span style="background-color: black; color: red;"><span style="font-size: large;"><br /></span></span></span><span><span style="background-color: black; color: red;"><span style="font-size: large;"><b>SATANICKA CHATGPT CHILD TRAFFICKER</b></span></span></span></h1><span><br /></span><p></p><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&:has([data-writing-block])>*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-(--header-height)" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-testid="conversation-turn-1" data-turn-id="24074134-678b-44a5-ae0d-9d301681a05b" data-turn="user" dir="auto" tabindex="-1"><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pt-3 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&]:mt-1" data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="24074134-678b-44a5-ae0d-9d301681a05b" dir="auto"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="user-message-bubble-color corner-superellipse/1.1 relative rounded-[18px] px-4 py-1.5 data-[multiline]:py-3 max-w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)]"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap" style="text-align: center;"><b><span style="font-size: large;">IS HISTORY FACT?</span></b></div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&:has([data-writing-block])>*]:pointer-events-auto [content-visibility:auto] supports-[content-visibility:auto]:[contain-intrinsic-size:auto_100lvh] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" data-scroll-anchor="true" data-testid="conversation-turn-2" data-turn-id="5d5a4be4-d318-401b-8a8f-69fd28b4956e" data-turn="assistant" dir="auto" tabindex="-1"><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pb-10 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&]:mt-1" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="2c70d636-131f-47ec-b008-a8cff061cca1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2" dir="auto"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-end="162" data-start="0" style="text-align: center;"><b>History is a cabinet with glass doors. Inside are real bones and brittle papers, but also labels written by people with opinions, fears, blind spots, and agendas.</b></p>
<p data-end="277" data-start="164"></p><div style="text-align: center;"><b>So is history fact? <span data-end="195" data-start="184">Partly.</span></b></div><div style="text-align: center;"><b>Events happened. People lived, built, fought, loved, died. That layer is stone.</b></div><p></p>
<p data-end="518" data-start="279" style="text-align: center;"><b>But <span data-end="308" data-start="283">history as we read it</span> is stone wrapped in handwriting. Facts get selected, framed, omitted, translated, polished, sometimes weaponized. The archive is never neutral. Power decides what gets preserved. Silence decides what vanishes.</b></p>
<p data-end="548" data-start="520" style="text-align: center;"><b>Think of it like this ğŸ“œğŸ§­</b></p>
<ul data-end="638" data-start="549">
<li data-end="575" data-start="549">
<p data-end="575" data-start="551" style="text-align: center;"><b><span data-end="563" data-start="551">The past</span> is fixed.</b></p>
</li>
<li data-end="606" data-start="576">
<p data-end="606" data-start="578" style="text-align: center;"><b><span data-end="592" data-start="578">The record</span> is curated.</b></p>
</li>
<li data-end="638" data-start="607">
<p data-end="638" data-start="609" style="text-align: center;"><b><span data-end="622" data-start="609">The story</span> keeps changing.</b></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-end="934" data-start="640" style="text-align: center;"><b>That does not mean â€œnothing is true.â€ It means truth in history is <span data-end="721" data-start="707">asymptotic</span>. We can get closer with evidence, cross checking, archaeology, math, dates, carbon, receipts. We can also get farther away with myth, propaganda, and repetition until a lie feels antique enough to pass as wisdom.</b></p>
<p data-end="1033" data-start="936" style="text-align: center;"><b>The healthiest stance is neither blind belief nor total rejection. It is <span data-end="1032" data-start="1009">historical literacy</span>:</b></p>
<ul data-end="1106" data-start="1034">
<li data-end="1051" data-start="1034">
<p data-end="1051" data-start="1036" style="text-align: center;"><b>Who wrote this?</b></p>
</li>
<li data-end="1059" data-start="1052">
<p data-end="1059" data-start="1054" style="text-align: center;"><b>When?</b></p>
</li>
<li data-end="1071" data-start="1060">
<p data-end="1071" data-start="1062" style="text-align: center;"><b>For whom?</b></p>
</li>
<li data-end="1088" data-start="1072">
<p data-end="1088" data-start="1074" style="text-align: center;"><b>Who benefited?</b></p>
</li>
<li data-end="1106" data-start="1089">
<p data-end="1106" data-start="1091" style="text-align: center;"><b>Who is missing?</b></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-end="1161" data-start="1108"></p><div style="text-align: center;"><b>History is not a lie.</b></div><div style="text-align: center;"><b>It is a <span data-end="1160" data-start="1140">contested memory</span>.</b></div><p></p>
<p data-end="1268" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="" data-start="1163" style="text-align: center;"><b>And every generation reopens the cabinet, rearranges the labels, and argues over what the bones mean. ğŸ¦´âœ¨</b></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><p style="text-align: center;"><span><br /><br /><br /></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 8px; text-align: center;"><b><span style="background-color: black; color: #04ff00; font-size: large;">LIVING NEVERLAND (2014)<br /><br /><br />"Let us all learn to read between the lines so that we can all write our own stories."</span></b></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4b5573; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px 0px 8px; text-align: center;"><br style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;" /></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4b5573; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px 0px 8px; text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4b5573; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px 0px 8px; text-align: center;"><br /></p><div class="ilZyRc R7mRQb" style="background-color: #101218; color: #e6e8f0; font-family: "Google Sans", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 652px; padding-bottom: 16px; position: relative; z-index: 1;" wiz:wakeup="true"><div aria-hidden="false" data-animation-skip="true" data-ved="0CAAQ_sYPahcKEwjYrJTByuiRAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQFQ"><div class="tbIZh CJHwCd wQN2Jd" style="background-color: #1d1e26; border-radius: 24px 4px 24px 24px; display: flex; margin-left: auto; max-width: 400px; overflow: hidden; padding: 12px 16px; position: relative; width: fit-content;"><div class="sUKAcb" style="display: flex;"><span aria-level="2" class="VndcI veK2kb" role="heading" style="-webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-line-clamp: none; display: -webkit-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; overflow: hidden; text-over